{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji27.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致陈云等电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致陈云等电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年8月17日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公债问题关系重大，请陈云立即回来向中央报告，加以讨论然后决定。同时，请饶、陈试探民建方面资本家的意见，电告我们。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]8月15日，陈云复电中央，对发行公债的数额、用途、利率和还本付息的时间等问题作了说明。这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的致陈云并告饶漱石、陈毅电的主要内容。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":8,"day":17}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":143,"page_end":143},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"陈云","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}